## Field Guidelines
- **theme**: Best match from Themes in Role Definition (e.g., "P&L & Financials", "Portfolio Strategy")
- **product**: Best match from Products: "Credit Cards (CC)", "Debit Cards (DC)", or "Cross-Portfolio (Both)"
- **project**: Specific initiative name (e.g., "Visa Infinite", "DC International") or "Ad-hoc" for one-off discussions
- **topic**: Best match from Topics, or generate a new one if strictly necessary
- **thread_name**: A concise, 5-word title capturing the essence
- **summary**: A 1-sentence summary of what was discussed/decided

